  Booysen has survived numerous attempts on his life in recent years, and rival gang bosses reportedly put a R5 million bounty on his head in December last year.
 
 
  
 
 
  The attack on Booysen at Melomed Hospital last year was the fourth in less than 12 months and his bodyguards managed to catch a man disguised as a female doctor, who allegedly tried to inject Booysen with snake venom.
 
 
  
 
 
